<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 12:32:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着伊朗战争的继续，迪拜加密货币活动 Token2049 被推迟</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/dubai-crypto-event-token2049-postponed-as-iran-war-continues</link><description>全球最大的加密货币会议之一 Token2049 将不再按计划在下个月举行迪拜活动，因为阿拉伯联合酋长国和其他中东国家面临着来自伊朗的持续导弹袭击。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iAz.AkbpC1bY/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 10:51:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/dubai-crypto-event-token2049-postponed-as-iran-war-continues</guid></item><item><title>中东紧张局势扰乱市场，比特币突破 72,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/bitcoin-edges-higher-in-asia-despite-middle-east-jitters</link><description>由于与伊朗的冲突没有减弱的迹象，比特币周五上涨，而石油价格徘徊在每桶 100 美元左右。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ij53fzFkmJOA/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 02:30:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/bitcoin-edges-higher-in-asia-despite-middle-east-jitters</guid></item><item><title>Tether 花费数十亿美元在华盛顿寻找新盟友</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2026-tether-usa-crypto-ambitions/</link><description>这家加密货币公司的亿万富翁首席执行官表示，在政府最高层的支持、1220 亿美元的美国国债和一家正在建设中的美国新企业的支持下，Tether 将继续存在。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iT6R8.a.9t2s/v3/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 10:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2026-tether-usa-crypto-ambitions/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行和渣打银行将在香港获得稳定币牌照</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/hsbc-standard-chartered-to-get-stablecoin-licenses-in-hong-kong</link><description>汇丰控股有限公司和渣打银行将成为香港首批获得许可的稳定币发行人之一，使香港的两家发钞银行在政府成为数字资产中心的努力中发挥核心作用。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igDAxrKVR_V0/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 05:09:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-13/hsbc-standard-chartered-to-get-stablecoin-licenses-in-hong-kong</guid></item><item><title>加密货币交易所押注预测市场以度过熊市</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-12/crypto-exchanges-eye-prediction-markets-stock-trading-to-survive-bear-market</link><description>要么做大，要么回家。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyP5aCxFbnMw/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-12/crypto-exchanges-eye-prediction-markets-stock-trading-to-survive-bear-market</guid></item><item><title>Tether Investment 首席执行官在主导交易热潮后辞职</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-12/tether-investments-chief-to-step-down-after-leading-deals-spree</link><description>Tether Holdings SA 首席投资官理查德·希思科特 (Richard Heathcote) 负责监督支持其主要稳定币的巨额储备，以及涉及从足球俱乐部到人形机器人等各种领域的交易热潮，他即将辞去职务。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iFyR5_uXgrOs/v0/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 18:44:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-12/tether-investments-chief-to-step-down-after-leading-deals-spree</guid></item><item><title>伊朗战争导致油价飙升至 100 美元以上，比特币走弱</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-12/bitcoin-weakens-as-oil-surges-back-above-100-on-iran-war</link><description>由于对伊朗冲突的担忧加深，油价短暂回升至每桶 100 美元以上，比特币波动接近近期价格水平。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/imyQrgW3agvE/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 04:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-12/bitcoin-weakens-as-oil-surges-back-above-100-on-iran-war</guid></item><item><title>尽管IPO规模达数十亿美元，但SPAC却很少有公司上市</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-11/spacs-take-few-companies-public-despite-11-7-billion-ipo-haul</link><description>在今年筹集了 117 亿美元资金的一系列 IPO 之后，一批新的空白支票公司加入了长队：所有其他工具都在等待将公司上市的机会。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ixKeTsNsxp.U/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 16:33:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-11/spacs-take-few-companies-public-despite-11-7-billion-ipo-haul</guid></item><item><title>Circle、币安加入万事达卡加密货币合作伙伴计划</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-11/circle-binance-join-mastercard-s-crypto-partner-program</link><description>万事达卡公司正在招募超过 85 家数字资产公司、支付提供商和金融机构，包括 Circle Internet Group Inc.、Binance 和 Gemini Space Station Inc.，加入一项新的全球合作伙伴计划，该计划旨在将加密支付与其网络保持连接，因为稳定币被宣传为传统支付轨道的替代品。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioYm_OchNHF4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 13:56:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-11/circle-binance-join-mastercard-s-crypto-partner-program</guid></item></channel></rss>